---
title: Sunshine Winter Chicken Salad with Grapefruit and Kale
description: Every bite of this salad will have you reminiscing about those hot summer days. Crunchy crisp kale, nutty toasted almonds, juicy tart grapefruit and creamy goat cheese. It's sunshine on a plate!

